            "image_1": "shopify://shop_images/6ad2d44bdbfb756d5b1e99fac3a5c749.jpg",
            "text_1": "<p>I recommend everyone the Uplift Facial Roller because it gently<strong> improve skin health</strong>. It stimulates circulation, r<strong>educes puffiness</strong>, and helps <strong>firm up the skin</strong>, especially around the<strong> jawline and eyes</strong>. Plus, it’s super easy to use—just roll it on your face for a quick, soothing treatment.</p>",
            "author_2": "<em>Author</em> [stars]",
            "text_2": "<p>Share positive thoughts and feedback from your customer.</p>",
            "author_3": "<em>Author</em> [stars]",
            "text_3": "<p>Share positive thoughts and feedback from your customer.</p>",
