            "content": "<ul><li><strong>24 Germanium stones </strong>- It <br/>provide gentle pressure on the skin to improve blood circulation and promote a vibrant glow.</li><li><strong>Aluminum Alloy handle </strong>- It is durable and easy to hold for long-term use. Its lightweight design makes it perfect for use at home, at the office, or while traveling</li></ul>",
