          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/09855382-de22-5211-ab29-0024cbfc5e39.jpg",
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>\"This thing is a game changer. I have a droopy side of my face as a side sleeper. One week of using this has entirely lifted that side of my face. It’s honestly nuts!\"</p>",
            "author": "- Lauren D."
          }
        },
        "testimonial_HMtQi7": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1459b15f-56b3-55df-846e-474681c69f11.jpg",
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>\"This uplift facial roller has become a staple in my beauty routine. It’s super easy to use, and I love how it instantly lifts and tones my skin.\"</p>",
            "author": "- Nikki R."
          }
        },
        "testimonial_xpigwP": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Skin_care_junkie_I_am_I_keep_my_nursejamiela_uplift_tool_in_the_car_since_I_spend_1-2_my_life_in_it_realtorlife_nursejamieuplift.jpg",
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>\"I take this wand everywhere! I use it in the middle of the day . The coldness of the wand helps reduce swelling and helps with the lymphatic system. Its relaxing. Im in ♥️with this!\"</p>",
            "author": "- Tara Y."
          }
        },
        "testimonial_yyRRp8": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/nursejamiela_nursejamie_nursejamieuplift_youtuber_beautyyoutuber_beautychannel_tatiapproved.jpg",
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>\"I can’t get enough of this tool! It helps relax my facial muscles, and I’ve seen a noticeable difference in my skin’s elasticity. It’s so therapeutic.\"</p>",
            "author": "- Erica Z."
          }
        },
        "testimonial_K9emEj": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Ok_guys_I_ve_found_something_that_s_too_good_not_to_share._And_if_I_m_late_to_this_party_please_excuse_this_busy_45-year_old_mom_who_is_just_trying_to_keep_up._Who_else_has_tried_this.jpg",
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>\"I rarely leave reviews but as someone who has been heavily dependent on ice rollers, and gua sha-- im pretty blown away by how much more effective this is in such a short amount of time. I LOVE THIS! </p>",
            "author": "- Victoria G."
          }
        }
